Package: MetaboDynamics
Title: Bayesian Analysis of longitudinal metabolomics data
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given="Katja",family= "Danielzik", email="katja.danielzik@uni-due.de", role = c("aut", "cre"),
